question: Which university is located in Tromsø, Norway?
true_answer: UiT Norges arktiske universitet (UiT The Arctic University of Norway).
answer: Trumsėje, Norvegijoje yra Šiaurės Norvegijos universitetas, dar žinomas kaip Tromsės universitetas (The Arctic University of Norway, UiT).
answer_translated_eng: Tromsø, Norway is home to the University of Northern Norway, also known as the University of Tromsø (The Arctic University of Norway, UiT).
